    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hRaK2",
      "x": 375,
      "y": 10340,
      "name": "Label D-Light 3",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 3 — Apricot Mist\n柔和杏色有机流动形状，奶油白底+暖桃光晕。\n圆润温柔，适合轻松亲和的界面。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "zOs3h",
      "x": 1655,
      "y": 10340,
      "name": "Label D-Light 4",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 4 — Rose Gold Haze\n玫瑰金+象牙色，带微妙金色光斑散景效果。\n奢华感但不沉重，适合高端产品页面。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "VLRkl",
      "x": 3035,
      "y": 10340,
      "name": "Label D-Light 5",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 5 — Vanilla Sunset\n香草色+淡落日橙，斜向光线条纹。\n温暖的黄金时刻感，适合首页hero区域。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "j0JJW",
      "x": 4415,
      "y": 10340,
      "name": "Label D-Light 6",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 6 — Champagne Silk\n香槟金+丝绸白，柔和光泽折射。\n如绸缎般高雅，适合品牌/奢侈品风格。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "CRF3Y",
      "x": 375,
      "y": 11260,
      "name": "Label D-Light 7",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 7 — Honey Dew\n蜂蜜色+奶油白，柔和波浪状丝绸流动。\n温暖而不抢眼，通用性强。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "zKPVu",
      "x": 1655,
      "y": 11260,
      "name": "Label D-Light 8",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 8 — Blush Cloud\n腮红粉+桃色云雾在奶油白上飘浮。\n水彩质感，柔美梦幻。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "xxnMo",
      "x": 3035,
      "y": 11260,
      "name": "Label D-Light 9",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 9 — Pearl Amber\n珍珠色+淡琥珀渐变，极度柔和。\n极简优雅，几乎透明的暖色调。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "NFAot",
      "x": 4415,
      "y": 11260,
      "name": "Label D-Light 10",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "content": "D-Light 10 — Soft Coral Breeze\n珊瑚粉+桃色波浪在奶油白上流动。\n优雅而有动感，适合创意展示页面。",
      "lineHeight": 1.6,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontWeight": "500"
    },
